39
00:02:02,980 --> 00:02:03,660
You...

40
00:02:03,860 --> 00:02:04,620
Mo Suqing.

41
00:02:05,420 --> 00:02:07,460
I hate scheming women like you the most.

42
00:02:07,980 --> 00:02:09,380
