Do you mean

46
00:02:15,100 --> 00:02:16,460
being nice to her in bed?

47
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:17,980
Mo Suqing, that's enough.

48
00:02:18,100 --> 00:02:19,180
As someone who works
in the media industry,

49
00:02:19,660 --> 00:02:20,860
you sneaked photos of others

50
00:02:21,220 --> 00:02:22,340
and distorted the truth.

51
00:02:22,460 --> 00:02:24,300
Apologize to Mr. Gu and your sister now.

52
00:02:24,300 --> 00:02:24,740
Humph.

53
00:02:27,980 --> 00:02:29,180
(Want me to apologize?)

54
00:02:35,780 --> 00:02:36,580
All right, Mr. Mo.

55
00:02:37,300 --> 00:02:38,820
