we can have the meal today.

56
00:02:38,820 --> 00:02:39,460
I'll leave now.

57
00:02:39,460 --> 00:02:40,260
Mr. Gu.

58
00:02:41,180 --> 00:02:42,900
Please stay. Calm down.

59
00:02:43,020 --> 00:02:44,220
Don't stoop to her level.

60
00:02:44,820 --> 00:02:45,860
