61
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:47,060
Please enjoy the meal first.

62
00:02:50,340 --> 00:02:52,060
You can have several days
to think about it.

63
00:02:52,860 --> 00:02:54,260
Come to me when you've come around.

64
00:02:56,460 --> 00:02:57,180
Jiannan.

65
00:02:57,420 --> 00:02:58,580
Mr. Gu, wait.

66
00:03:03,180 --> 00:03:03,860
Look at you.

67
00:03:03,860 --> 00:03:05,540
Look at what you have done.

68
00:03:07,060 --> 00:03:08,340
Don't you know how much

69
